{"results":[{"aya":"050","id":1852,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"我的刑罚确是痛苦的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"051","id":1853,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"你应当对他们叙述易卜拉欣的客人们的故事。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"052","id":1854,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"当时，他们进去见他，说：祝你平安。他说：我们确是畏惧你们的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"053","id":1855,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他们说：你不要畏惧，我们的确以一个聪明的男孩向你报喜。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"054","id":1856,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：我已老迈，你们还向我报喜吗？你们以什么向我报喜呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"055","id":1857,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他们说：我们凭真理而向你报喜，所以你不要绝望。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"056","id":1858,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：除迷误者外，谁会绝望于真主的恩惠呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":15,"previousPage":"/zh/s015-7.json","nextPage":"/zh/s015-9.json"}}